OL,5, Electrical goods retailer Currys has   
OL,6, rejected a takeover approach from US   
OL,7, investment firm Elliott.               
OL,9,FCurrys, which operates more than 800   
OL,10,Fstores globally and employs 28,000     
OL,11,Fpeople, said the offer valued the      
OL,12,Fbusiness at about #700m.               
OL,14,FBut the proposal "significantly        
OL,15,Fundervalued" the company, Currys said. 
OL,17,FElliott has a reputation as an activist
OL,18,Finvestor, meaning it pursues companies 
OL,19,Fin order to take them over and change  
OL,20,Fhow they are run.                      
